PHP::Session::DBI
=================

Interface to PHP DataBase Sessions.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

      PHP::Session 0.26
      DBI          0

and this module is recommended:

      DBD::mysql   0

All are available on CPAN.

